
Overview of noun formula

The noun formula has 7 senses (first 5 from tagged texts)
                                        
1. (8) formula, expression -- (a group of symbols that make a mathematical statement)
2. (6) recipe, formula -- (directions for making something)
3. (3) formula -- (a conventionalized statement expressing some fundamental principle)
4. (1) formula, chemical formula -- (a representation of a substance using symbols for its constituent elements)
5. (1) convention, normal, pattern, rule, formula -- (something regarded as a normative example; "the convention of not naming the main character"; "violence is the rule not the exception"; "his formula for impressing visitors")
6. formula -- (a liquid food for infants)
7. rule, formula -- ((mathematics) a standard procedure for solving a class of mathematical problems; "he determined the upper bound with Descartes' rule of signs"; "he gave us a general formula for attacking polynomials")
